×031MEGA Updates×
×031============×
19th of April this year, IRIS staff (hi 
there old fossils ;-))  announced  that 
their new homepage  for  Eurochart was finished.  You 
could almost smell how proud they were...  With   all 
rights though.

Yes  we  are  talking  updates  in  size XXL from the
website  ×031www.eurochart.dk.×  It  is  constructed  by a
member  called  Hexagon  who  has  done  a  great job
